INSERT INTO `reviews` VALUES (1,3,53,5,'nice','2025-11-24 08:42:52'),(2,4,53,3,'It was a nice book but not my type','2025-11-24 08:53:03'),(4,5,53,4,NULL,'2025-11-24 08:53:50'),(5,2,53,5,'it was nice book','2025-11-24 08:56:59'),(6,2,7,4,'One of the amazing books I have read','2025-11-24 09:03:52'),(7,6,53,4,NULL,'2025-11-24 10:19:52'),(8,6,58,3,'too much of fantasy...far from reality','2025-11-24 10:22:08'),(9,3,10,5,'OMG!!! It\'s one of the best horror books i have \"ever\" read....I suggest everyone to try this one if you loovvveeeeee horror','2025-11-24 17:57:01'),(10,2,5,4,NULL,'2025-11-25 06:53:01'),(11,2,26,5,'Felt Goosebumps!!!','2025-11-25 06:53:50'),(12,2,4,4,'Currently reading Sapiens by Yuval Noah Harari, and wow, itŌĆÖs already blowing my mind.\r\nHarariŌĆÖs way of explaining human evolution, belief systems, and how societies formed is so clear and fascinating.\r\nWill update once I finish!','2025-11-25 06:55:52'),(13,7,56,3,'A poignant story set during Partition, but the emotional connection felt a bit limited for me.\r\nKhushwant Singh captures the chaos and brutality of the time very realistically, and the setting is incredibly vivid.\r\nHowever, I couldnŌĆÖt fully connect with the characters, and some parts felt slow.\r\nA good, important read ŌĆö just not a personal favourite.','2025-11-25 07:11:08'),(16,9,82,5,NULL,'2025-11-25 07:17:00'),(17,10,90,5,'oo god!!! the chase.....','2025-11-25 07:25:21'),(18,10,91,5,'I need my Christian Harper so badddd.......','2025-11-25 07:26:46'),(19,11,18,2,'Finished Steve Jobs.\r\nWell-researched but too long and too dry for me.\r\nI struggled to stay engaged, and the narration felt repetitive at times.\r\nA 2-star read.','2025-11-25 07:30:41'),(20,17,24,5,'I watched this disaster unfold in real time. Way too much angst, zero communication, and an unhealthy amount of emotional damage. Alex is terrifyingly devoted, Ava is too forgiving, and somehow it still works. Would I recommend this love story? maybe. Did I survive it? Barely.','2026-03-29 08:46:13'),(21,17,91,4,'ŌĆ£I knew Christian was dangerous, but watching him fall in love wasŌĆ” unsettling. He loves quietly, obsessively, and with terrifying patience. Stella deserved better communication, but somehow she chose him anyway. Do I trust him? No. Would I stand between them? Also no. I value my life.','2025-12-25 16:37:25'),(22,18,88,5,'love this book.........','2026-01-09 17:25:52'),(23,21,101,5,'loved it......','2026-02-28 15:25:39'),(25,18,91,5,'ŌĆ£ItŌĆÖsŌĆ” actually a really interesting story. Stella meets this man, Christian, and heŌĆÖs very calm, very put-togetherŌĆöthe kind of person who always seems in control. And he really cares about herŌĆ” in a very intense way.\r\n\r\nI think Stella feels safe with him, and that matters a lot. Even ifŌĆ” sometimes the way he loves is a little overwhelming.\r\n\r\nItŌĆÖs not a perfect kind of love, but itŌĆÖs real in its own way. And if Stella is happy, then I think thatŌĆÖs what counts most.ŌĆØ','2026-03-29 08:53:26'),(26,18,89,5,'Ugh, BridgetŌĆÖs life is literally insane ? Like imagine being a whole princess and falling for your bodyguard?? And not just any bodyguardŌĆöthat man. The tension?? I was living for it.\r\n\r\nFrom my POV, her story is way more intense than mine. ItŌĆÖs all stolen moments, ŌĆ£we shouldnŌĆÖt do this,ŌĆØ and him being all cold but secretly obsessed with her. And Bridget?? She really had to grow up fast and carry a whole country on her back while dealing with feelings like that. I was stressed for her.','2026-03-29 09:03:43'),(27,17,89,5,'Ugh, BridgetŌĆÖs life is literally insane ? Like imagine being a whole princess and falling for your bodyguard?? And not just any bodyguardŌĆöthat man. The tension?? I was living for it.\r\n\r\nFrom my POV, her story is way more intense than mine. ItŌĆÖs all stolen moments, ŌĆ£we shouldnŌĆÖt do this,ŌĆØ and him being all cold but secretly obsessed with her. And Bridget?? She really had to grow up fast and carry a whole country on her back while dealing with feelings like that. I was stressed for her.','2026-03-29 09:09:01');
